pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.utilities

Class GenericAsyncTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.utilities.GenericAsyncTask

  • public class GenericAsyncTask
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides async tasks for the insertion of every model type. An insertion of many items at a time in the main thread causes the app to crash. So every insertion is handled through an extra thread.
